OL,3,CFirefighters battle 'ongoing' 200-
OL,4,Ctonne commercial waste fire
OL,6,FFirefighters are still battling a 200-
OL,7,Ftonne commercial waste fire in Port
OL,8,FTalbot a day on since the blaze
OL,9,Fstarted.
OL,11,FIn an update on Thursday (30 April),
OL,12,FMid and West Wales Fire and Rescue
OL,13,FService (MWWFRS) confirmed that its
OL,14,Fcrews remain on the scene at the blaze
OL,15,Fon Dock Road in Port Talbot, which
OL,16,Fcrews first responded to on Wednesday
OL,17,Fafternoon (29 April).
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
