OL,3,CFirefighters battle 'ongoing' 200-
OL,4,Ctonne commercial waste fire
OL,6,FThe service said crews have been
OL,7,Fmaking "steady progress" overnight and
OL,8,Fhave been "actively firefighting and
OL,9,Fmonitoring hotspots."
OL,11,FSome road closures are still in place
OL,12,Fin the area to allow emergency service
OL,13,Faccess.
OL,15,FThe service has advised residents to
OL,16,Favoid the area, and to keep windows
OL,17,Fand doors closed if smoke is present.
